div.p:
He, who shall not be shaken by these stormes, is built upon a Rock;
               Luke 6. 48. 1 Cor. 10. 4. Mat. 16. 18.
               nay he is a Rock, (Petra fortis frangit, non frangitur) a member of Iesus Christ, of that spirituall Rock, against which the gates of hell shall never prevaile.
